<i>¶ Waterfalls and tikis</i>
<i>guard the hidden doors ¶</i>

23:16.129 --> 23:21.365
¶ To a pirate hangout made
from shipwrecks washed ashore ¶

23:21.367 --> 23:23.634
<i>¶ Tunnels and secret doors </i>

23:23.636 --> 23:26.504
<i>¶ Slide aways</i>
<i>through the floor ¶</i>

23:26.506 --> 23:29.140
