23:29.142 --> 23:31.609
¶ Pulleys and counterweights

23:31.611 --> 23:36.614
<i>¶ It's a hideout in disguise</i>
<i>A palm tree covered isle ¶</i>

23:36.616 --> 23:39.483
<i>¶ To make sure that old</i>
<i>Feather Hat ¶</i>

23:39.485 --> 23:42.186
<i>¶ Stays away </i>

23:42.188 --> 23:46.424
<i>¶ Pirate Island hideout </i>

23:47.492 --> 23:51.429
<i>¶ Pirate Island hideout </i>

23:52.431 --> 23:54.932
<i>¶ A hideaway out on the sea </i>

23:54.934 --> 23:57.368
<i>¶ A Never Land mystery </i>

